a personalized AI chatbot using DeepSeek model! This chatbot provides motivation, productivity hacks, career advice, and emotional well-being tips – all in a sleek, modern UI.
🔹 Workflow:
1️⃣ User inputs a query 📩
2️⃣ AI processes it using DeepSeek-R1 🤖
3️⃣ Context-aware responses generated via LangChain 🔗
4️⃣ Displayed in an intuitive Streamlit UI 🎨
